    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="namespaceOSUSat" kindref="compound">OSUSat</ref> Structured Logging System. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A lightweight logging framework designed for embedded systems with limited resources. Stores log entries in a ring buffer for deferred transmission.</para>
<para>Features:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Multiple severity levels (DEBUG through CRITICAL)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Automatic timestamp and source line capture</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Component-based organization</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Generic flush interface via callbacks (transport-agnostic)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Ring buffer storage with overwrite support</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Printf-style formatting </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
